<h1 class=element-invisible>Welcome to Salford Software</h1>
<div class="region region-content">
<div id=block-block-1 class="block block-block">
<h2>Our solutions</h2>
<div class=content>
<p><a class=identity-management href=identity-management> </a> <a class=user-experience href=user-experience> </a> <a class=tools href=tools> </a> <a class=infrastructure href=infrastructure> </a> <a class=cloud-services href=cloud-services> </a> <a class=professional-and-technical-services href=professional-and-technical-services> </a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div id=block-block-7 class="block block-block">
<h2>Our approach</h2>
<div class=content>
<p>Salford Software specialises in identity &amp; access management and infrastructure solutions to ensure that the right people, have the right access to the right systems at the right time. Our solutions are delivered by the best technical people in the business and our experience has shown that business process analysis is just as important as the technology.</p>
<p>Using proven delivery methodology and approach, Salford Software continues to successfully deliver solutions which help to improve efficiency, security and the user experience by successfully tailoring the correct technology to any market or customer.</p>
<p><img alt="" src="sites/default/files/resize/our-approach-400x112.png" style="width:400px;height:112px" width=400 height=112 /></p>
</div>
</div>
