<div class="views-field views-field-title"> <span class=field-content><a href="events/office-365-and-beyond">Office 365 and beyond</a></span> </div>
<div class="views-field views-field-field-date-and-time"> <span class=field-content><span class=date-display-single property=dc:date datatype=xsd:dateTime content="2013-03-21T09:45:00+00:00">21-Mar-2013</span></span> </div>
<div class="views-field views-field-body"> <div class=field-content><p><span style="color:#333;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;line-height:1.5em">If you are in the process of migrating or transitioning to <a href="http://salfordsoftware.co.uk/microsoft-office-365">Office 365</a> or have already moved to Office 365, read on!</span></p></div> </div>
