<div id=views_slideshow_cycle_main_product_tab_slider-block class="views_slideshow_cycle_main views_slideshow_main"><div id=views_slideshow_cycle_teaser_section_product_tab_slider-block class="views-slideshow-cycle-main-frame views_slideshow_cycle_teaser_section">
<div id=views_slideshow_cycle_div_product_tab_slider-block_0 class="views-slideshow-cycle-main-frame-row views_slideshow_cycle_slide views_slideshow_slide views-row-1 views-row-odd">
<div class="views-slideshow-cycle-main-frame-row-item views-row views-row-0 views-row-first views-row-odd">
<div class="views-field views-field-body"> <div class=field-content><h3>How it works</h3>
<p>Salford Software has developed a solution that enables institutions providing their students with Microsoft collaboration tools, like Live@edu and Microsoft Office 365, to deliver an even better user experience.  CalSync provides a single view of their personal calendar appointments and their student timetable.</p>
<p>Using CalSync students can access their calendars whilst on the move with a comprehensive view of all the day’s activities and location, whenever and wherever they are.</p></div> </div>
<div class="views-field views-field-field-tab-image"> <div class=field-content><img typeof=foaf:Image src="sites/default/files/styles/product_tab_img/public/products/calsync.png" width=230 height=200 alt=""/></div> </div>
<div class="views-field views-field-view-node"> <span class=field-content><a href=calsync>Read more...</a></span> </div></div>
</div>
<div id=views_slideshow_cycle_div_product_tab_slider-block_1 class="views-slideshow-cycle-main-frame-row views_slideshow_cycle_slide views_slideshow_slide views-row-2 views_slideshow_cycle_hidden views-row-even">
<div class="views-slideshow-cycle-main-frame-row-item views-row views-row-0 views-row-first views-row-odd">
<div class="views-field views-field-body"> <div class=field-content><h3>What does ARMS do?</h3>
<p>Salford Software’s <strong>Advanced Records Management System</strong> (ARMS) provides a web based interface for the management and maintenance of user information. ARMS is an authoritative source for user accounts creating and providing life-cycle management for user services and resources without compromising security.</p></div> </div>
<div class="views-field views-field-field-tab-image"> <div class=field-content><img typeof=foaf:Image src="sites/default/files/styles/product_tab_img/public/products/arms_screenshot_Firefox__Access_Keys_%28Administrator%29.png" width=230 height=200 alt="" title=ARMS /></div> </div>
<div class="views-field views-field-view-node"> <span class=field-content><a href=arms>Read more...</a></span> </div></div>
</div>
<div id=views_slideshow_cycle_div_product_tab_slider-block_2 class="views-slideshow-cycle-main-frame-row views_slideshow_cycle_slide views_slideshow_slide views-row-3 views_slideshow_cycle_hidden views-row-odd">
<div class="views-slideshow-cycle-main-frame-row-item views-row views-row-0 views-row-first views-row-odd">
<div class="views-field views-field-body"> <div class=field-content><h3>How it works</h3>
<p>Our Cobra solution helps to improve the way that your institution engages and communicates with students, enhancing their experience whilst studying. It helps to address the challenges faced by students and staff across the university or college and has been developed to enable collaboration and efficient working, whenever and wherever.</p></div> </div>
